<span id="freeTextContainer16977020500257726643">This is about as spiritual as I get. A five star book for me is something that at any point throughout life if I saw the book i would love to pick it up and read it at any point of the book. The 121 meditations are wide ranging from the “woah I should try that” to the “that seems so obvious wish I had thought of that”. It&apos;s pretty verbose, but I like Ohso&apos;s writing and guidance.</span>
